Package ePortfolio

Class Investment

java.lang.Object
ePortfolio.Investment
Direct Known Subclasses:
MutualFund, Stock
public abstract class Investment extends Object
The class is the parent class which has two children classes, mutualfund and stock. The investment class holds the values that both children class need for theit investments. There are also some general computations that are in this class.
